1
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,039
You just said this wasn't yours,

2
00:00:18,039 --> 00:00:19,280
and now you say it's missing.

3
00:00:20,359 --> 00:00:22,839
Why don't you bring your maid here?

4
00:00:22,839 --> 00:00:25,399
Why did you try to kill me?

5
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:31,879
Please spare me!

6
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,520
Lady Zhou forced me!

7
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,399
She gave me 50 taels of silver

8
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:36,399
and took my father,

9
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,240
making me switch your incense!

10
00:00:38,719 --> 00:00:39,359
Nonsense!

11
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:41,000
When did I ever give you money?

12
00:00:41,399 --> 00:00:42,079
You ungrateful girl,

13
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:42,880
slandering me like this!

14
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:44,439
You have no family wealth,

15
00:00:44,439 --> 00:00:45,520
no personal property,

16
00:00:45,679 --> 00:00:47,840
all your money comes from this household.

17
00:00:48,719 --> 00:00:49,240
Check the accounts,

18
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:51,159
and the truth will be revealed.

19
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:52,439
My lady, I didn't!

20
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:54,159
It's Madam Yin who's stirring up trouble!

21
00:00:54,479 --> 00:00:55,840
She must be holding a grudge against me

22
00:00:56,079 --> 00:00:57,240
for making up these lies!

23
00:00:57,479 --> 00:00:59,039
I have no grudges against you,

24
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,679
yet you tried to kill me.

25
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:02,679
Are you afraid I'll uncover the truth?

26
00:01:03,719 --> 00:01:05,239
Have you forgotten

27
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,879
that night when you tried to kill me,

28
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:08,599
you said to me yourself

29
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:09,920
that I was the one

30
00:01:10,439 --> 00:01:12,560
who ruined your future?

31
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:14,480
What do you have to say now?

32
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,599
My lady, I was wrong!

33
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,480
I was blinded by greed,

34
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:20,599
and I listened to others' schemes to poison and seize power.

35
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:23,480
I attacked Madam Yin because I feared she would expose me,

36
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,200
and I would be unable to stay in the household.

37
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:27,840
My lady, for my years of service,

38
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,799
please forgive me this once.

39
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:30,280
I will never do it again!

40
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,719
You poisoned your mistress,

41
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,400
and attacked someone with a knife.

42
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:36,760
According to the law,

43
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:38,560
you deserve to be executed.

44
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,359
Take her away.

45
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:43,879
Why?

46
00:01:44,359 --> 00:01:46,000
Why were you born as the wife of the Minister,

47
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,719
living a life of luxury,

48
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:47,480
and having people to pamper you?

49
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:49,599
I served you diligently for three years,

50
00:01:49,599 --> 00:01:51,159
yet I don't even have a proper title.

51
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,799
It's all because you blocked my way.

52
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,040
It's all because of you!

53
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:56,760
Lady Shen seems unfazed.

54
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,439
This secret dungeon

55
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,319
has only one guard.

56
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:20,639
When he opens the door,

57
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:22,039
you smear these chili peppers

58
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:23,520
into his eyes.

59
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,840
Then we can escape.

60
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,280
Is anyone there?

61
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,400
Help!

62
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:39,080
Someone, please!

63
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,360
Hello?

64
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,280
What's going on?

65
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,479
Madam Su is poisoned!

66
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,439
Come and check her!

67
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,319
Hurry up!

68
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,280
What are you waiting for?

69
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,240
Sister Su!

70
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,240
Sister Su!

71
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,120
Come on!

72
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,400
Sister Su, go!

73
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,120
Sister Su!

74
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:01,840
Run!

75
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:03,439
Sister Su!

76
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,240
Run!

77
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,240
Sister Su!

78
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,520
Sister Su!

79
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,240
Sister Su!

80
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,400
You go first.

81
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:13,879
Get help.

82
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,400
Go!

83
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,120
Go!

84
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:20,879
Go!

85
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:29,879
Today,

86
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:32,120
I declare to the neighbors,

87
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,639
Shen Yuan

88
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,039
is a man without conscience,

89
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,159
who favors concubines over his wife,

90
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,759
who beats his wife,

91
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,360
and who imprisoned my women's clinic.

92
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:47,639
What are you doing?

93
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,680
Who are you?

94
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:50,759
Shen Yuan,

95
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:52,599
Your servant assaulted

96
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,360
a healer,

97
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,639
damaged my clinic,

98
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,280
and imprisoned my female patients.

99
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,120
If you

100
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:03,599
don't release them today,

101
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,719
tomorrow,

102
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:07,039
I'll let the whole Chang'an know

103
00:04:07,599 --> 00:04:10,360
how the Shen residence abuses its power.

104
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,159
How dare a woman

105
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:15,000
be so arrogant here?

106
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:16,480
How dare you

107
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,720
question my actions?

108
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:18,759
Guards!

109
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:20,639
Get this madwoman out of here!

110
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:21,879
Stop!

111
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,519
I'm from the Supreme Court!

112
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:26,680
So, it seems

113
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,639
what she said is true.

114
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,720
I don't care who you are!

115
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:52,040
I want you dead!

116
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,920
Who let you in here?

117
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,000
Do you have official permission?

118
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:00,279
This is the inner court of officials.

119
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,639
It's not a place for you to rampage.

120
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,519
Where are Su Yi and Lin Yange?

121
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,560
I always act

122
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,120
without considering the consequences.

123
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,759
If you don't know,

124
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:12,759
get out of here.

125
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,240
But if you know

126
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:18,240
and don't tell me,

127
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:20,120
delaying my rescue,

128
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:23,879
I'll tear you apart

129
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,120
and bury you with them.

130
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:26,639
They're...

131
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:27,480
in the dungeon.

132
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,199
I don't know anything else.

133
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:30,759
Lead the way.

134
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,720
Take her.

135
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,160
Yes.

136
00:05:53,879 --> 00:05:54,759
Shen Yuan can't run far.

137
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:55,879
He must be in the secret passage.

138
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:02,160
Sister Su.

139
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,519
Sister Su, let's go.

140
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,399
Slow down.

141
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,000
Go.

142
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,000
You bitch.

143
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,120
Don't run.

144
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,000
Yan Ge.

145
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:40,199
Yan Ge.

146
00:06:42,879 --> 00:06:43,639
Yan Ge.

147
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,759
Sister Su.

148
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,639
Are you okay?

149
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:48,480
I'm fine.

150
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:52,879
You've suffered.

151
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:53,959
Come.

152
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,040
He got away.

153
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,240
There must be another secret passage.

154
00:07:01,519 --> 00:07:02,240
Xinyue.

155
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:03,680
Your clothes.

156
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,240
I'm fine.

157
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:04,839
Go.

158
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:06,680
What's wrong with you?

159
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:08,519
Go.

160
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,079
Xinyue!

161
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,000
Xinyue!

162
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:28,120
The wound has been torn

163
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,680
and not treated in time,

164
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:33,600
causing the ulcer to rupture

165
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:34,800
and a sudden fever.

166
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:36,079
And...

167
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:37,399
And what?

168
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,399
She

169
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:40,199
is

170
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,879
poisoned.

171
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,040
How is that possible?

172
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:48,759
The only way now

173
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,680
is to keep her alive temporarily.

174
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,680
Let's see

175
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,920
if she can make it through these days.

176
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,360
Don't worry, My Lady.

177
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:02,040
It's odorless and tasteless.

178
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,319
No one will ever find out.

179
00:08:16,959 --> 00:08:17,639
Go check on her.

180
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,120
Yes, My Lady.

181
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:24,759
No!

182
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,079
Father, no!

183
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,600
Father!

184
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,560
It's okay now.

185
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,560
It's okay.

186
00:08:34,639 --> 00:08:36,000
How is Madam Yin?

187
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:41,919
Xinyue!

188
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:43,480
Xinyue!

189
00:08:45,159 --> 00:08:46,000
Doctor!

190
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:46,759
Call the doctor!

191
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:48,759
Yunzhou,

192
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:50,679
take this token

193
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:52,320
and go to the Imperial Court to find my brother.

194
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:54,279
Tell him to bring

195
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:56,200
the best royal physician from the palace.

196
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:00,960
What's wrong?

197
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,039
Go!

198
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:04,440
Ms Yin's life is in danger.

199
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,879
What are you waiting for?

200
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:11,200
Nong,

201
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,000
do as she said.

202
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,559
He's just a servant,

203
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,240
why would my brother care?

204
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,240
Yunzhou,

205
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:19,519
Ms Yin's life is at stake,

206
00:09:20,039 --> 00:09:20,919
go now!

207
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:23,879
Go!

208
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,120
May I try?

209
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:34,399
Who are you?

210
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,600
How can we trust you?

211
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:40,679
Ms Yin was poisoned with a Persian toxin.

212
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,480
Ordinary healers can only treat the surface,

213
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,519
but I can cure the root cause.

214
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,399
Do you know

215
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:51,679
the importance of gender separation?

216
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,840
She's my future daughter-in-law.

217
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,879
Disregarding propriety

218
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,480
is not the act of a gentleman.

219
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,159
Madam.

220
00:09:59,639 --> 00:10:00,480
For me,

221
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,320
studying medicine is to save lives,

222
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:03,399
not to harm.

223
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:05,000
Since I'm here,

224
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,919
I can't just stand by and do nothing.

225
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:09,840
Enough.

226
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,519
If we let the rules

227
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:12,600
delay the treatment,

228
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,000
that would be harming her.

229
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:19,120
He's right.

230
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,879
Then,

231
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:22,360
please, doctor,

232
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:24,919
do your best to cure my daughter-in-law.

233
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,639
Men and women are different.

234
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:42,720
Yan Ge,

235
00:10:43,399 --> 00:10:44,159
do it for me.

236
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,759
You can take it out now.

237
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:01,759
My lord,

238
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:03,320
you can come in now.

239
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:06,720
Within three days,

240
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,759
you need to do it again.

241
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:08,480
Otherwise,

242
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:09,840
she may be in danger.

243
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,240
Apply this daily

244
00:11:15,519 --> 00:11:16,120
to reduce bruising.

245
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,000
Now Shen Yuan

246
00:11:28,399 --> 00:11:29,120
is no longer a threat.

247
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:31,399
With someone looking after the residence,

248
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:32,919
you two

249
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,720
can stay here for now.

250
00:11:37,679 --> 00:11:38,679
With you two by her side,

251
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,399
she'll be happier.

252
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:44,480
Thank you, my lord.

253
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,360
Two rooms have been prepared

254
00:11:46,799 --> 00:11:48,720
for you two to rest.

255
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:49,480
Nong,

256
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:51,679
take good care of them.

257
00:11:52,559 --> 00:11:52,919
Yes.

258
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:10,720
My Lord,

259
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:12,279
the Matriarch requests your presence.

260
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:23,519
My Lady,

261
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,120
have you ever resented the world?

262
00:12:29,759 --> 00:12:32,000
It would be a lie to say no.

263
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:34,519
I resent my mother's absence,

264
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,720
the capriciousness of fate,

265
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,960
and the limitations of medical knowledge.

266
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,159
But if one indulges in hatred,

267
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,399
is like holding a knife to my own throat.

268
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:46,440
It hurts me the most.

269
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,519
You've been

270
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,519
such a sensible child.

271
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:01,360
Why are you so stubborn

272
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:03,600
when you grow up?

273
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,480
Even if you save her,

274
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,720
what good will it do?

275
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,480
I study medicine to save myself.

276
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,759
I save lives in front of me,

277
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,639
and let go of the obsession in my heart.

278
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,360
What do you mean by that?

279
00:13:18,039 --> 00:13:19,840
I know you're as pure as snow,

280
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,919
but snow on the eaves

281
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,399
can't last long.

282
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,759
The world is full of hidden dangers,

283
00:13:26,759 --> 00:13:27,879
and people are treacherous.

284
00:13:27,879 --> 00:13:29,360
How long can you keep

285
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,279
saving others?

286
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,519
You don't need

287
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,360
to get involved in this anymore.
